得取餐码，此种方式等于分文未付骗取了一份套餐。 发现这个漏洞后，徐某“喜出望外”。从当年4月起，除了自己这样点餐操作，徐某还做起了“副业”：将诈骗得来的套餐产品通过线上交易软件低价出售给他人，从中获利。 同时，他还与同学有“福”同享，将犯罪方法当面或通过网络传授给丁某等4名同学。截至同年10月案发，徐某的行为造成百盛公司损失5.8万余元，丁某等四人造成百盛公司损失0.89万元至4.7万元不等。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig6XvmMyX6qA6EAMaCDY0MjQ5ODI3IJHc6IQGMHw4nB1AA3IJNDU4ODYyNTQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1021 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-21c1a1c56c3678f0c3c0f019affd4919_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1620789462.1439536","card_id":"Q_458864077","target":{"id":458864077,"title":"武汉大风中吊篮撞楼两人死亡，家属称「事发前工人曾电话求救，赶到后遭围殴抢手机」，还有哪些细节值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/458864077","type":"question","created":1620717571,"answer_count":307,"follower_count":2420,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,5582,6792,13599,24317],"comment_count":51,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"5月10日，武汉极端天气中发生惊险一幕，两名工人不幸离世。 “事发前他们曾电话求救。”5月11日，一名遇难工人家属杨先生告诉封面新闻，事发前弟弟曾电话求救称项目停电，吊篮停止运行。事发3小时，家属才得到通知，后赶到现场，发现死者遗体被扔在17楼水泥地，家属还遭遇围殴抢手机。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig6XvmMyX6qA6EAMaCDY0MjUwMTU3IIPg6IQGMDM49BJABHIJNDU4ODY0MDc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"740 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-051ee6780be640ed6d52318db9c27d45_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1620789462.1447713","card_id":"Q_458770659","target":{"id":458770659,"title":"如何看待某剧组在南京大学拍戏遇冷，学生不围观、不追星？这一现象反映了什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/458770659","type":"question","created":1620660486,"answer_count":465,"follower_count":1118,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1718,4421,5619,7819,11594],"comment_count":48,"is_following":false,"e